===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|grc|πολύγλωττος||many-tongued, polyglot}}, Attic form of {{m|grc|πολύγλωσσος}}, from {{m|grc|πολύς||many}} + {{m|grc|γλῶττα||tongue, language}}. {{affix|en|poly-|-glot}}.

